{"title":"远行","authors":["段和平"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"远行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"段和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在急促地喘息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烘托一种氛围，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我即将远行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在为我而涌动的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惜别的浪潮中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一双白鸽般美丽的小手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一排雄健的青铜手臂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在许许多多飘飞的头发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与挥舞的眷恋之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不会凋谢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已获得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种深深的慰藉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生，骤然变作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月的雨滴……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}